name: Mictlantecuhtli
description:
Lord of the Mictlan(The Manssion of the dead). 

Digital illustration of the God of the underworld and the shadows, The one who has Starry eyes and fumes out of his body, one obsidian pedernal in a hand, and the rest of the dead in another, a human skulls collar, black feathers instead of hair and owls as bad omen birds around him.
